He decended down lower, circling a certain spot. He spotted an arm, that looked like KitKat&#39;s design. He swooped down and landed. He looked at it. It had wolf fur on it. 

He decided to make a chance with this one and take it back ot KitKat. He flapped his wings, and grabbed the arm with his feet. He caught a wing current and lifted himself higher into the air.



